Red Eye;;64;;79;;PG-13;;In the wake of her grandmother's funeral, hotel manager Lisa Reisert (Rachel McAdams) is waiting to fly back home when she meets charming Jackson Rippner (Cillian Murphy) at check-in. She thinks it luck that they're seated together on the plane, but soon learns otherwise. Jackson hopes to assassinate the head of Homeland Security, but to do so, he needs Lisa to reassign the official's room number at her hotel. As insurance, Jackson has kidnapped Lisa's father (Brian Cox).;;Mystery & thriller;;Wes Craven;;2005;;Rachel McAdams,Cillian Murphy,Brian Cox,Jayma Mays,Jack Scalia,Kyle Gallner,Carl Gilliard,Laura Johnson,Max Kasch,Loren Lester,Monica McSwain,Brittany Oaks,Angela Paton;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1149496-1149496-red_eye